Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:

New construction - late 2021 completion - just minutes to the hospitals, CBD and airport. 

A variety of ground and first floor sizes, layouts and inclusions which can be modified to suit. 
+ Areas from 100sqm - 200sqm - 400sqm up to 1000sqm. 
+ Freehold and strata office or medical suites available

individual needs

+ Internal partitioning and floor coverings available by separate negotiation
